                        <persName role="scribe" ref="PRS00000">Ḫāyla ʾIyasus, ʾAfa Warq (Gabra
                           Śǝllāse)</persName>Additio 1 mentions brothers rǝʾǝsa dabr Ḫāyla ʾIyasus
                        and märigeta ʾAfa Warq whose baptismal name is Gabra Śǝllāse as the scribes.
                        However, it the presense of two hands cannot be immediately
                           confirmed.<date>Late 19th - early 20th century.</date>
